{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida95e82d0-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2272"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2272"},"text":"§ 2272.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Space science and technology strategy: coordination","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Defense and the Director of National Intelligence shall jointly develop and implement a space science and technology strategy and shall review and, as appropriate, revise the strategy biennially. Functions of the Secretary under this section shall be carried out jointly by the Under Secretary of Defense for Research and Engineering and the official of the Department of Defense designated as the Department of Defense Executive Agent for Space.","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002083"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002083"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See Transfer of Functions note below."}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ida95e82d1-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/136/dA/tIX/s911/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–136, div. A, title IX, § 911(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2003-11-24"},"text":"Nov. 24, 2003","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/117/1563"},"text":"117 Stat. 1563","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/84/dA/tIX/s911/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–84, div. A, title IX, § 911(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":"–(3), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2009-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 2009","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/123/2428"},"text":"123 Stat. 2428","children":[],"tail":", 2429; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/383/dA/tIX/s901/j/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–383, div. A, title IX, § 901(j)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-01-07"},"text":"Jan. 7, 2011","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/4324"},"text":"124 Stat. 4324","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/92/dA/tXVI/s1604"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–92, div. A, title XVI, § 1604","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-11-25"},"text":"Nov. 25, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/1098"},"text":"129 Stat. 1098","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92/dA/tIX/s902/28"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–92, div. A, title IX, § 902(28)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2019-12-20"},"text":"Dec. 20, 2019","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/133/1546"},"text":"133 Stat. 1546","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"ida95e82d2-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"ida95e82d3-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"ida95e82d4-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 2272, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041"},"text":"act Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/70A/124"},"text":"70A Stat. 124","children":[],"tail":", related to contracts to obtain designs submitted in design competitions, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/160/dA/tVIII/s821/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–160, div. A, title VIII, § 821(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-11-30"},"text":"Nov. 30, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/1704"},"text":"107 Stat. 1704","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"ida95e82d5-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2019—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–92","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Under Secretary of Defense for Research and Engineering” for “Assistant Secretary of Defense for Research and Engineering”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2015—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/92"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–92","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally. Prior to amendment, section consisted of subsecs. (a) to (c) relating to space science and technology strategy, required coordination, and definitions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2011—Subsecs. (a), (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/383"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–383","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Assistant Secretary of Defense for Research and Engineering” for “Director of Defense Research and Engineering” wherever appearing."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2009—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/84/s911/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–84, § 911(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “The Secretary of Defense and the Director of National Intelligence shall jointly develop” for “The Secretary of Defense shall develop”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(2)(D). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/84/s911/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–84, § 911(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", added subpar. (D)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/84/s911/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–84, § 911(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", amended par. (5) generally. Prior to amendment, par. (5) read as follows: “The strategy shall be available for review by the congressional defense committees.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"ida95e82d6-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"ida95e82d7-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2011 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/383"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–383","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-01-01"},"text":"Jan. 1, 2011","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/383/s901/p"},"text":"section 901(p) of Pub. L. 111–383","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s131"},"text":"section 131 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"ida95e82d8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For termination and transfer of functions of the Department of Defense Executive Agent for Space, see ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/91/s1601/b/1"},"text":"section 1601(b)(1) of Pub. L. 115–91","children":[],"tail":", set out as a Termination of Certain Positions and Entities note under former "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2279a"},"text":"section 2279a of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"ida95e82d9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Initial Report","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/84/dA/tIX/s911/a/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–84, div. A, title IX, § 911(a)(4)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2009-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 2009","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/123/2429"},"text":"123 Stat. 2429","children":[],"tail":", required the first space science and technology strategy required to be submitted under former "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2272/a/5"},"text":"10 U.S.C. 2272(a)(5)","children":[],"tail":" to be submitted on the date on which the President submitted to Congress the budget for fiscal year 2012 under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105"},"text":"31 U.S.C. 1105","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
